Thank you for practice teacher üôè With the theme of freedom and forgiveness, my goal today (and hopefully every day) will be to remember that when I meet a difficult person: they don't necessarily have conflict with me as much as they have conflict within themselves. The best thing to do for ourselves, and for them, is to let their energy flow past us. Paraphrasing Nietszche, we become like the monsters we fight. Arguing and indecision is wasted energy that requires us to take away from our own spirit and energy. Create (positivity) don't hate! Namaste üôè
